    public class TopTrumpsMenu
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.io.Serializable
    Instantiable class which defines a TopTrumpsMenu. This class implements the ActionListener interface to button clicking events as well as JMenu selection events.

    • Constructor Detail

      • TopTrumpsMenu

        public TopTrumpsMenu()
        TopTrumpsMenu no-argument constructor. Sets some default values for the Menu as well as creating JButtons and JMenus. First action is to initialise a Clip and provide the Menu with music. Contains exception-handling code.
